# App release files

These files must stay in sync. Full workflow: [.cursor/skills/app-release/SKILL.md](../skills/app-release/SKILL.md).

**Required on every release**

1. `src/version.js` — `VERSION` (source of truth)
2. `CHANGELOG.md` — top `## [X.Y.Z] - YYYY-MM-DD` entry
3. `README.md` — `Current release: vX.Y.Z` **and** shields version badge

**When SEO-relevant**

4. `llms.txt` — `## Last updated` date matches changelog
5. `sitemap.xml` — `<lastmod>` dates match changelog

**Before finishing**

```bash
make lint && make test
```

One commit per release. Do not commit unless the user asks.
